snippet.title: Smash Drums x Le Frickin' Rock Show - Official Update Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Watch the trailer for Smash Drums to see what to expect with the latest free update for the VR and MR rhythm game. The Smash Drums x Le Frickin' Rock Show update trailer showcases various game modes like Classic mode, Arcade mode, and Fusion mode. Smash Drums' free mixed reality and VR update is available on the Meta Quest Store today, June 26, 2024.
